%p Creating a gem is easy! Just follow these steps:
%ul
  %li Sign up for an account on Gemcutter.
  %li Create your gem. Get started with Jeweler.
  %li Make sure you're running RubyGems 1.3.3.
  %li Install the gemcutter gem with: <code>gem install gemcutter</code>
  %li Run <code>gem upgrade</code> to use Gemcutter as your main RubyGem source.
  %li Build your gem with: <code>gem build yourgem.gemspec</code>
  %li Push it! <code>gem push yourgem-0.0.1.gem</code>
